Package marketplace.Handlers

Class OrderHandler

java.lang.Object
marketplace.Handlers.OrderHandler
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class OrderHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
Handler class for Order object type. Handles methods that main methods for interacting with Order type. Interacts with ACTIVE_BUY_ORDERS, ACTIVE_SELL_ORDERS tables in database.
